{"tid":609364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不戴口罩等於自殺！ 北京發布沙塵藍色預警AQI 999","createTime":"2018-03-29T03:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T07:21:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"5e641390ab67b3bbaac1060fcb132742e949cb29","tid":609364,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/114634_135ce5759c9dd1f02862758edd1cb903.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F114634_135ce5759c9dd1f02862758edd1cb903.png&h=cd675bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國北京今天霾害嚴重，其空氣品質指數（AQI）飆到999「嚴重汙染」，天空一片霧濛濛。<br />\n北京市氣象台今天也發布「沙塵藍色預警信號」，指出受上游沙塵天氣影響，預計今天北京將出現浮塵天氣，能見度較低，請注意防範，同時這也是今年的首個沙塵預警，據國家環保部數據，截至7時北京空氣質量為嚴重污染，首要污染物為PM10，濃度達1181微克/立方米。<br />\n一名在北京的鄉民在PTT上發文，指出今天北京早上都不亮，並酸說「結果發現不是天不亮，原來是北京啟動了防雷射系統禦敵了...」。<br />\n對於北京的空氣品質，不少中國網友在微博發文，有人認為，今天天氣不戴口罩等於自殺，「空氣中有種說不出味道，感覺在下土一樣，在辦公室一樣很難受」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2378774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2378774&d=JLGd5SMmZQlcxDcZtRERjzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d0d4a464\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2378774&h=119b8e52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2378774</a>"},{"pid":"7bf299ce849de2a05ea2a935e124263401cc1d35","tid":609364,"uid":17799,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"6b751365d8f85c5f45d015f2c9cec7493042f830","tid":609364,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"D空氣會係咩味？"},{"pid":"5a6c671fedacaba3c51b4f0901700dcc9b83a5fb","tid":609364,"uid":15880,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:50:10.000Z","msg":"開反衛星系統進行核試<